
NAME

	runcronjobs

PREREQUISITES

	The following modules are needed :
		
		MIME::Entity
		Config::General
		Config::General::Extended
		Dir::Which 
		Set::Groups

	To install them, run the following commands:
	
		perl -MCPAN -e 'install MIME::Entity'
		perl -MCPAN -e 'install Config::General'
		perl -MCPAN -e 'install Config::General::Extended'
		perl -MCPAN -e 'install Dir::Which'
		perl -MCPAN -e 'install Set::Groups'

INSTALLATION

	To install this program, run the following command:

		tar xfz runcronjobs*.tgz
		cp runcronjobs /usr/bin
		cp runcronjobs.conf-sample /etc/runcronjobs.conf
		
	then edit /etc/runcronjobs.conf and customize the configuration.

SUPPORT AND DOCUMENTATION

	After installing, you can find documentation for this module with the perldoc command:

		perldoc runcronjobs

	You can also look for information at:

		http://math.univ-angers.fr/runcronjobs

